rule-11-12-a.test_description: A one story single zone building has service water heating systems. The building runs for 24 hours a day and has service hot water heating loads.
rule-11-12-a.expected_raised_message_includes: This building is a 24hr-facility with service water heating loads

standard.ruleset_reference: Table G3.1 #11, baseline column, d + exception
standard.rule_description: For large, 24-hour-per-day facilities that meet the prescriptive criteria for use of condenser heat recovery systems described in Section 6.5.6.2, a system meeting the requirements of that section shall be included in the baseline building design regardless of the exceptions to Section 6.5.6.2
